_pdbx_database_remark.id 999
_pdbx_database_remark.text
;SEQUENCE
Residue B SER 608 and Residue B VAL 701 are not linked.
Distance of C-N bond is 6.15. Residue B THR 384 and 
Residue B ASN 601 are linked together.
The residues 600-1008 of chains B and D were modelled 
as alanines due to poor electron density.  The residue 
names were assigned arbitrarily as there are multiple 
possible sequences consistent with the density, 
and the connectivity is unclear.
;
